Package: Temporal
Title: Parametric Time to Event Analysis
Date: 2026-03-14
Version: 0.3.0.3
Author: Zachary McCaw [aut, cre] (ORCID: <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2006-9828>)
Maintainer: Zachary McCaw <zmccaw@alumni.harvard.edu>
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Zachary",
